Download the zip file and extract it.
Open the extracted "mpouriew" folder, click on the address bar, type "powershell", and press Enter.
In the PowerShell window that opens, paste this command and press Enter:powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File setup-pdfjs.ps1
Open Chrome and go to chrome://extensions
Turn on "Developer mode" (top-right toggle).
Click "Load unpacked" and select the "mpouriew" folder.
Enjoy!
